# Hyperapp Gizmo

[![Travis CI](https://img.shields.io/travis/hyperappJS/hyperapp-gizmo/master.svg)](https://travis-ci.org/hyperapp/hyperapp-gizmo) [![npm](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/hyperapp-gizmo.svg)](https://www.npmjs.org/package/hyperapp-thin) [![Slack](https://hyperappjs.herokuapp.com/badge.svg)](https://hyperappjs.herokuapp.com "Join us")

Hyperapp Gizmo (use @hyperapp/gizmo if this is an [organization](https://www.npmjs.com/org/hyperapp) module) is a mischievous creature, higher-order-app, helper library, unary function or whatever for [Hyperapp](https://github.com/hyperapp/hyperapp). The following bullet list is optional. If you feel you don't need it, then don't bother.

